# Draft:Aishwarrya Khanna

----
Aishwarrya Khanna
Aishwarrya khanna is an Indian actress, who has appeared in many serials, music videos, web series and Bollywood and Tollywood movies (1992)
Personal Life
Aishwarrya Khanna was born in Bhopal, Madhya Pradesh, India. She did her schooling and her bachelors from Delhi. Later, she moved to Mumbai to pursue her career in acting and bagged her first assignment, which was aired on Sony national television in serial CID.
Career
Aishwarrya Khanna had started her career with CID serial on Sony entertainment. Then she grabbed many music videos with Zee Music, Times Music, Punjabi Music Video like Pehli mulakaatein, rozanna, jaate hue pal, izhaar, tere bina, naya parinda and many more.
She did advertisement for government of Uttar Pradesh, India for women help and safety ‘shaktipari bano har naari’ and Mumbai police. Other advertising include with star sports, jumboking, mannat jewellers and some south television advertisement for sarees, jewellers and so on and so forth.
She did serials with Daman Mitti Ka, CID, Aahat, Shapath, Yeh hai Aashique, PMS, Supercops vs Supervillans, Emotional Atyachar and Saath Nibhana Saathiya.
[https://m.timesofindia.com/topic/Aishwarrya-Khanna Aishwarrya] has done many web series as main lead. Some of the series include The Internet Affair, Safar, Mr. Khadus, baby & babe and more to come.
Adding to the list Aishwarrya also worked in movies which include Noor, Dilliwaliyaan. She has done a Telugu movie in Hyderabad named ‘1992’.
Apart from this she has also done various modelling assignments and ramp shows.
